    <entry>
      <title>HTML教程-链接</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/25/HTML%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/25/HTML%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B-%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="HTML初级教程"><a href="#HTML初级教程" class="headerlink" title="HTML初级教程"></a>HTML初级教程</h1><p>今天我们来讲链接</p><h2 id="链接（介绍）"><a href="#链接（介绍）" class="headerlink" title="链接（介绍）"></a>链接（介绍）</h2><p>相信大家都应该见过链接这种东西吧！就是这个<a href="#">有下划线的一般是蓝色的</a>东西</p><p>链接的作用有很多种，包括但不限于以下</p><blockquote><p>跳转网页</p><p>下载文件</p><p>转到某个标题位置</p><p>标记网站中的图片</p><p>……</p></blockquote><p>接下来就让我们看看如何在网页中插入一个链接吧！</p><h2 id="链接（使用）"><a href="#链接（使用）" class="headerlink" title="链接（使用）"></a>链接（使用）</h2><p>废话不多说，直接上代码</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">href</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>web<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>文本<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>注：可以把web替换为以下：</p><blockquote><p>网页地址(<a href="http://xxx.com/">http://xxx.com</a>)</p><p>#本页已标记的标题</p><p>文件地址</p><p>mailto:邮箱地址</p></blockquote><p>语法2(#~)细节:</p><p>这种用法指跳转至一篇文章的某个标题处,你需要在这个标题处命名,如下</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>名字<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>标题文字<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>然后使用链接方法如下</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">href</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>#名字<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>链接文字<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>如何使用图片代替链接文字?</p><p>你可以使用以下代码</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">href</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>web<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>图片地址<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>怎么样让链接变成其它颜色?(蓝色在黑身背景下不好区分)</p><p>这个需要运用CSS的知识,我们以后再说~</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
