      <title>HTML教程-入门与文本</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/23/HTML%E5%88%9D%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/23/HTML%E5%88%9D%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="html初级教程"><a href="#html初级教程" class="headerlink" title="html初级教程"></a>html初级教程</h1><p>作者：Ntsc</p><h2 id="入门"><a href="#入门" class="headerlink" title="入门"></a>入门</h2><p>HTML是目前网页前端(服务器端)最常用的一种语言,属于标记语言,所以在学习使用没有编程语言那么困难</p><h2 id="标记"><a href="#标记" class="headerlink" title="标记"></a>标记</h2><p>HTML是一种标记语言，标记放在&lt;&gt;中<br>标记也有两种——单标记（空标记）与双标记</p><pre><code>&lt;ab&gt;  //单标记&lt;ab&gt;&lt;/ab&gt;  //双标记</code></pre><p>那网页中的文本呢?</p><pre><code>网页中的文本一般都放置在双标记的中间例子:&lt;p&gt;文本&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre><p>当你理解了这些后,恭喜你,成功入门了</p><h2 id="网站基本框架"><a href="#网站基本框架" class="headerlink" title="网站基本框架"></a>网站基本框架</h2><p>废话不多说,直接上代码</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token doctype">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span>  //声明<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>html</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> //表示文件开始<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>头部信息<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>网页内容<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span> //表示文件结束</code></pre><p>你需要牢记这个框架,代码绝大多数会在”头部信息”与”网页内容”中编写</p><h2 id="文本I"><a href="#文本I" class="headerlink" title="文本I"></a>文本I</h2><p>以下介绍一些代码</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>之间写文本,表示一个段落,在末尾会自动换行<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>表示标题1,数字可以替换为1~6<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>这是一个单标记,作用是换行,包括但不限于文本,图片</code></pre><h2 id="文本II"><a href="#文本II" class="headerlink" title="文本II"></a>文本II</h2><p>以下我们会介绍文字处理,例如加粗,斜体</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>strong</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>加粗<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>strong</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>big</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>大号<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>big</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>i</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>斜体<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>i</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>small</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>小号<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>small</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>sub</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>上标<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>sub</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>sup</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>下标<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>sup</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>这些代码看作与文本紧密相连的部分</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
